reviewText: cartoons were great, quailty excellant. grand daughter love the lunch bucket . brought so very goog smiles to everyone who saw them

Video quality is awful, awful, awful! Product discription is misleading because it lists some popular cartoons, but the majority are not. I would have returned it but, the postage would have been more than the purchase price. The tin was worth the sale price. I wouldn't suggest purchasing this item.
